(defun w3m-make-ccl-coding-system
  (coding-system mnemonic docstring decoder encoder)
  "Define a new CODING-SYSTEM by CCL programs DECODER and ENCODER.
CODING-SYSTEM, DECODER and ENCODER must be symbol."
